<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Forespent" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Forespent,</orth> 1) previously bestowed: <cit><quote>his goodness f. on us,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 2.3.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 3, 64</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) past, foregone: <cit><quote>his vanities f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.4.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 4, 36</bibl></cit>.
<lb />3) exhausted: <cit><quote>almost f. with speed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 1, 37</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>f. with toil,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.3.1" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 3, 1</bibl></cit> (M. Edd. <emph>forspent</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>